{
  "page": "Realm of the Jhogwin",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:WorldofIceandFire.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Realm of the Jhogwin is located in The Known World\"><img alt=\"Realm of the Jhogwin is located in The Known World\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/10/WorldofIceandFire.png/300px-WorldofIceandFire.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/10/WorldofIceandFire.png/450px-WorldofIceandFire.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/10/WorldofIceandFire.png/600px-WorldofIceandFire.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 40%; left: 70.3%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Realm of the Jhogwin\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: -6.5em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Realm of the Jhogwin</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">The <a href=\"/index.php/Known_world\" title=\"Known world\">known world</a> and the location of the Realm of the Jhogwin\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>The <b>Realm of the Jhogwin</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaf_realm_of_the_jhogwin.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaf_realm_of_the_jhogwin.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> or <b>Realm of Jhogwin</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiaf_central_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiaf_central_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> is a mountainous region of northern <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>, situated within the northernmost part of the <a href=\"/index.php/Krazaaj_Zasqa\" title=\"Krazaaj Zasqa\">Krazaaj Zasqa</a>. It is roughly northeast of <a href=\"/index.php/Vaes_Dothrak\" title=\"Vaes Dothrak\">Vaes Dothrak</a> and east of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingdom_of_the_Ifequevron\" title=\"Kingdom of the Ifequevron\">Kingdom of the Ifequevron</a>, with the island of <a href=\"/index.php/Far_Ib\" title=\"Far Ib\">Far Ib</a> to the north. To the southeast are the <a href=\"/index.php/Howling_Hills\" title=\"Howling Hills\">Howling Hills</a>.\n</p><p>Its name in the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki_language\" title=\"Dothraki language\">Dothraki language</a> refers to the <a href=\"/index.php/Jhogwin\" title=\"Jhogwin\">Jhogwin</a>, the stone <a href=\"/index.php/Giants\" title=\"Giants\">giants</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> legends.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaf_realm_of_the_jhogwin.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaf_realm_of_the_jhogwin.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Bones of the ancient Jhogwin can be found in the mountains.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_bones_and_beyond.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_bones_and_beyond.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Realm_of_the_Jhogwin&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\">